UKhozi FM music Compiler and radio presenter, Khetha Gwala has been retrenched. The news was confirmed by the acting Spokesperson of SABC, Mmoni Seapolelo. In a brief statement, she wrote: "The SABC can confirm that Mr. Khetha Gwala is affected by the Section 189 process‚Äù. Khetha joined Ukhozi FM as one of the music compilers in the late 1990s. This after winning the DJ Competition. Over the years he built his name and became one of the leading presenters within the station. Some of the slots he presented include Top 20 and Party Time on Saturdays from 18:00 to midnight. He also did the Magazine programme on Thursdays and Fridays, from 19:00 to midnight.